headline: How Recent Developments Are Rewriting the Story for KeyCorp
summary: KeyCorp's consensus analyst price target was recently revised downward, slipping modestly from $21.65 to $21.46. This subtle adjustment comes as experts weigh the company's robust revenue outlook against emerging valuation concerns. Positive drivers are being balanced by ongoing expense pressures.
